## Quality gates (new ones on top of pass 1 gates)

- Shirt MUST look visually 3D with depth, not a flat extruded shape — cylinder body minimum
- Uploading an image to "Front" MUST show it covering the front face of the shirt visibly
- Uploading a DIFFERENT image to "Back" MUST show it covering the back face when shirt is rotated
- "Auto-fit" button MUST visibly re-center and scale the image on click
- Transform sliders MUST update the shirt texture in real time (no lag > 100ms)
- WebGPU badge appears only when `navigator.gpu !== undefined` — not hardcoded
- Color picker still works (solid color on body when no image uploaded)
- Pattern presets still work (when no image uploaded)
- Existing features: back text, cart, save&share — all still functional
- Zero console errors on first paint
- GLB load attempt MUST have a try/catch with graceful fallback (no white screen on 404)

