## Risks

- Free shirt GLB URL availability: the three attempted URLs may all 404. If so, proceed immediately to procedural fallback (CylinderGeometry half-shells). Do not waste time on URL hunting beyond 3 attempts.
- WebGPU model download: `segformer` is ~50MB — do NOT eagerly import. The deterministic smartAlign must work without it. WebGPU path is additive only.
- Front/back split with cylinder approach: seams at theta=0 and theta=PI must be clean (no visible gap). Use slight overlap (5 degrees) on each half to avoid z-fighting.
- Transform sliders + real-time updates: texture matrix updates in r3f must trigger via state change. Use `useMemo` keyed on transform values so the texture recalculates only when controls change.

